<Content>Good Value Hotel Quiet, spotlessly clean hotel, very quiet and really good value for money. We were staying to go to athletics at the Olympic Stadium which is 2 stops away on the S-Bann. 10 minute walk to Spandau which has a pretty old town - there was a wine festival on while we were there - lots of different German wines and some interesting (!) bands playing... Would stay again if in the area. 
